          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the cbse pattern schools catering to tranferees in verious public sector employees children. my son Koushik vaidhinathan studied here from std VI to X . I cannot rate this very good but definitely o.k. You can admit without donation . teachers are of good quality. For us from BOI colony at Nerul the school was 3-4 kms away so we found it convenient. The children become street smart learning everything good and bad.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
