            "name": "Tuhin Purkait"
          },
          "datePublished": "2018-02-25",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am a 2010 pass out student. I studied here from class 8-10(cbse). Its a centrally sponsored school(I guess). It is the best school of my life(I did my schooling from 4 different schools). The teachers are too good. Their dedication is unparalleled. You are bound to respect  them throughout your life. Mannohar mam(is my most favourite mam), Jolly mam, Kanchana mam, Bose mam, our principal Kalavati mam all were too good. I am  grateful to all these teachers.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
